item.title: CVE-2021-36294|2024-09-16T16:22:50.056Z -- dell -- vnx%20control%20station
item.description: Dell VNX2 OE for File versions 8.1.21.266 and earlier, contain an authentication bypass vulnerability. A remote unauthenticated attacker may exploit this vulnerability by forging a cookie to login as any user.
